== Get Started  ==

Welcome to Integration group, here are some steps might help you to get started:

* Navigate through Integration wiki page and OpenDaylight project pages (check links below)
* Think about which task/deliverable you would like to contribute
* Sign up for discuss, infrastructure and integration-dev mail lists [https://lists.opendaylight.org/mailman/listinfo here]
* Send mail to above lists to introduce yourself
* Jump on #opendaylight on freenode IRC ([http://webchat.freenode.net/ webchat]) to listen real time OpendayLight discussions

